data.description: Beautiful 4 sided brick, 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home with finished daylight basement. 2.3 acre lot with wrap around driveway and side entry garage. Large kitchen with new appliances. Spacious master bedroom on main level. Master bath features his/her sinks, jacuzi tub, and large walk-in closet. New AC units and hot water heater. Two separate living areas, office, media room, rec room. and workshop in garage. Tons of house for the money. Owner is relocating and highly motivated to sell!
